title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 140: Featuring Theo Fleury, Cal Petersen and Matt Luff
description:
On Thursday's episode of Spittin' Chiclets the guys have two great interviews on tap. The boys are joined by Theo Fleury to talk about his career, his sobriety, some great stories and a ton more. The guys are also joined by a few of the LA Kings young guys (Cal Petersen, Matt Luff) to talk about dating apps in Los Angeles. The guys also go around the league and talk about some NHL news and discuss what the Sabres should do about Jeff Skinner.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
